name: BAD JOKES
description:
Series of single-page, photo-copied, original line drawings accompanied by pithy texts that humourously represent Billington's perspective on pop culture and life.

Includes original hand drawn cover. Signed.

name: THINKING PAIN
description:
NUMBER 2!
Billington continues to serve up wry observations with "Thinking Pain". In this collection of line drawings; a proposal for a new Canadian flag, 3-D bar graph elucidations, warm words of reception, among others.

Includes original drawing on front cover. Signed.

name: MY NEW FRENCH BLOUSE
description:
THICKEST ONE YET!
Free hand line drawings relate all manner of idiosyncratic observations approaching the banal and absurd. Highlights include drawings of/for a prescription turtle-neck, Phd comparison and the ideal dog.

Includes orginal drawing on front cover. Signed.
